snippet.title: inviZimals™: Shadow Zone Gameplay Trailer E3
snippet.description:
Check out the trailer for inviZimals(R): Shadow Zone and get ready to continue the hunt for those hidden creatures that only your PSP system can see! With new inviZimals to catch, co-op play and the ability to mutate and customize your creatures, prepare to travel the world and embark on a thrilling new adventure!
